OL,3,CJoey Barton kicked wife in head during
OL,4,Cdrunken row at home, court told
OL,6,FFormer footballer Joey Barton pushed
OL,7,Fhis wife to the floor before kicking
OL,8,Fher in the head during a drunken row
OL,9,Fat their family home, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FGeorgia Barton was left with a lump on
OL,13,Fon her forehead and a bleeding nose
OL,14,Fafter the alleged assault. Friends
OL,15,Fwere forced to intervene in the
OL,16,Fargument between the pair, pulling
OL,17,FBarton away from his wife, prosecutors
OL,18,Fsay.
