OL,3,CJoey Barton kicked wife in head during
OL,4,Cdrunken row at home, court told
OL,6,FThe former Man City and QPR
OL,7,Fmidfielder, 42, is accused of
OL,8,Fassaulting Georgia Barton, 38, in Kew,
OL,9,Fsouth-west London in June 2021, where
OL,10,Fthey had been drinking with two other
OL,11,Fcouples while their children slept
OL,12,Fupstairs.
OL,14,FThe arguing had started after Barton
OL,15,Fthreatened to fight his wife's brother
OL,16,Fand father, Westminster Magistrates'
OL,17,FCourt heard.
OL,19,F"There had been a verbal disagreement
OL,20,Fabout a family matter," prosecutor
OL,21,FHelena Duong said.
