OL,6,FBarton ` who appeared in court wearing
OL,7,Fa dark coat, dark jumper, jeans and
OL,8,Fglasses ` "grabbed her and pushed her
OL,9,Fto the ground and kicked her in the
OL,10,Fhead", Ms Duong said.
OL,12,FAs a friend tried to intervene, Barton
OL,13,F"threw" him off and said "don't
OL,14,Fdisrespect me", the trial heard.
OL,16,FMrs Barton called the police shortly
OL,17,Fafter 11pm to "report she had been hit
OL,18,Fby her husband", the court heard.the
OL,19,Fpair had both drunk "four or five
OL,20,Fbottles of wine", a previous hearing
OL,21,Fwas told.
