OL,3,CJoey Barton kicked wife in head during
OL,4,Cdrunken row at home, court told
OL,6,FDuring the 999 call played to the
OL,7,Fcourt, a tearful Mrs Barton told the
OL,8,Fcall handler: "Me husband's just hit
OL,9,Fme in the house.
OL,11,F"He's in the house, I'm outside."Asked
OL,12,Fif anything similar had happened
OL,13,Fbefore, she said: "No, it's the first
OL,14,Ftime," adding that she had been hit
OL,15,F"in the face".
OL,17,FWhen police arrived at around 11:30pm,
OL,18,FMrs Barton told them: "I've been
OL,19,Fpushed down and kicked about and
OL,20,Fstuff. He said he was going to fight
OL,21,Fwith my brother and my dad."
