OL,3,CJoey Barton kicked wife in head during
OL,4,Cdrunken row at home, court told
OL,6,FThe former footballer, of Widnes in
OL,7,FCheshire, was due to face trial at a
OL,8,Fmagistrates' court in 2022, but the
OL,9,Fcase was adjourned after Mrs Barton
OL,10,Fsent a letter to prosecutors
OL,11,Fretracting her allegations.
OL,13,FA judge then ordered that proceedings
OL,14,Fbe paused over concerns a trial would
OL,15,Fbe unfair to Barton after prosecutors
OL,16,Fsaid they did not plan to ask Mrs
OL,17,FBarton to give evidence in court.
