OL,3,CJoey Barton kicked wife in head during
OL,4,Cdrunken row at home, court told
OL,6,FThe Director of Public Prosecutions
OL,7,F(DPP), Stephen Parkinson, appealed
OL,8,Fagainst the decision at the High Court
OL,9,Fin London, with barristers claiming at
OL,10,Fa hearing that a fair trial could go
OL,11,Fahead.
OL,13,FIn a judgment in June, two senior
OL,14,Fjudges ruled in the DPP's favour and
OL,15,Fsaid Barton should face a trial over
OL,16,Fthe allegations in front of a
OL,17,Fdifferent judge.
